    "code": "def findMedianSortedArrays(nums1, nums2):\n    merged = sorted(nums1 + nums2)\n    n = len(merged)\n    if n % 2 == 1:\n        return float(merged[n // 2])\n    else:\n        return (merged[n // 2 - 1] + merged[n // 2]) / 2.0\n",
